{"tid":844935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★潮漲溺斃外判工 來港僅數個月 兒子於深圳居住","createTime":"2018-10-02T09:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T09:56:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c15636b6f9f366faa0dce3bf93f5e27370826b4","tid":844935,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】一名漁護署外判清潔工人，前日於流浮山尖鼻嘴清除海桑時溺斃，遺下妻子及年僅4歲兒子。死者遺孀透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫來港僅數個月</span>，於有關外判公司任職僅3個月，日薪700多元，獨力養起妻兒及外家，死者曾向妻子指平日工作要上山下海，更需到水深及胸位置工作。事故後，勞工處已勒令即時停工，直至另行通知；漁護署則表示會向死者家屬提供援助。工業傷亡權益會質疑外判公司沒向死者提供安全設施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181002/large/a0801a.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181002%2Flarge%2Fa0801a.gif&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c8be76af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181002/large/a0801a.gif</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181002/20512611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F20512611&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=5f6cbeb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F20512611&h=de0b3392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181002/20512611</a>"},{"pid":"2b5faa6223df19ee7ce71d7e8a69c0cfddf287e0","tid":844935,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\